goals.text: Have a dedicated weekly date night with my partner.
goals.why: Protected connection time keeps our relationship playful, aligned and grateful.
goals.nextStep: Block one night per week as sacred, arrange childcare if needed, and plan the first month.
goals.reward: Book a surprise weekend away after eight straight weeks.

goals.text: Build a lean, strong body that gives me energy for everything else I want to do.
goals.why: When I feel strong and energetic, everything else in life gets easier.
goals.nextStep: Block out regular training times in my calendar and stick to them.
goals.reward: Buy myself new gear or book a session after 6 weeks of consistency.

goals.text: Build $250,000 per year in passive income.
goals.why: Passive income creates total freedom for travel, experiences and family time.
goals.nextStep: Model my income strategy and set quarterly acquisition targets.
goals.reward: Celebrate each major milestone with a special experience or dinner.
